                  <summary>Maṣḥafa gǝṣṣǝw “Lectionary for the entire year”&#xD; I) Blessing prayer,
                     Barǝkännä ʾǝgziʾo… “Bless us, Lord…” (fols. 3ra-4va)&#xD; II) Scriptural
                     readings for liturgical periods, fasts and feasts for the entire year (fols.
                     5r-30v).</summary>
